'''John Livesey''' (died [[2022]]) was an actor of the [[BBC|BBC Repository Company]]'s core cast. He voiced several roles in the [[The Lord of the Rings (1981 radio series)|1981 radio series of ''The Lord of the Rings]]'': [[Otho Sackville-Baggins]], [[Éothain]], a [[Ruffians|Ruffian]] and an unspecified bit part.
